Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:16.42,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:28.92,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why have I gone back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:32.89,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, sir, you don't seem to be feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:34.20,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:36.89,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, sir, you seem to have a stomachache.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:38.71,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't soil yourself, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:45.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't... remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:49.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So it's like none of it ever happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:53.15,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:02.16,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, you shouldn't try to move so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:08.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, damn it?! \NEverything reset again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:10.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Including my promise with Emilia!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:34.09,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,You entered without even knocking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:36.55,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,What a rude one you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:38.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:41.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me stay here for a bit, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.90,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,There was last time and again now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:46.82,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,How are you breaking \Nthrough my Door Crossing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:50.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Beatrice...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:51.68,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Addressing me with no title, I suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:55.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You said I broke through your Door Crossing \N"last time" and "now," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:02:00.14,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I just teased you about it, three or four \Nhours ago, for being so insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:04.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If this is the second time I've \Nwoken up in the mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:07.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then you remember me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:11.27,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,If I could, I'd rather erase you \Nfrom my memory, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:15.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So the conditions are \Ndifferent from last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:18.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The save point's changed from \Nnear the guy with the appas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:20.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,to the two angelic girls in maid uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:22.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,How did I die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:25.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was normal before I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:30.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even after I fell asleep, I wasn't in any \Nsituation I felt might be fatal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:35.16,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered what you were muttering about, \Nand I hear all this about living and dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:38.13,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,By human standards, discussing such things \Nis boring and senseless, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:42.05,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you'll only get \Nlies and abusive speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:48.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, you were a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:49.90,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:54.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, seeing that your attitude \Nnever changes calms me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:58.20,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Only an ultimate pervert would be \Ncalmed by verbal abuse, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:01.03,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving, I suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:04.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I want to double check something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait until afterward to get depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.99,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.93,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:22.91,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely shining...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:26.59,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.58,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Ram and Rem were in a frenzy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.37,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,saying you disappeared \Nright after you woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:34.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that... I got held \Nup by Beatrice for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:39.55,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Again? I heard she played a trick on \Nyou before you woke up, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:42.57,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:45.07,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:48.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, your adorable eyes,\N ears, nose, and mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:53.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:56.16,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:57.63,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You protected me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.95,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:02.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I feel great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:04.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little low on blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,all my mana was stolen,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:08.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,the shock of waking up sapped my strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:11.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and I feel like my mind's taken \Na fatal beating with a bat,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:15.12,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that's g— Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:17.77,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that mean you're hurt all over?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:20.86,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Subaru... Great morning, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.99,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I can't thank you enough for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.37,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I have to thank you somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:30.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let me pet your fur whenever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:31.68,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:35.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our time is limited, and our world is grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:41.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And Emilia-tan's and my story \Nhas only just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:42.72,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,True...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.68,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.18,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the "tan" come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:49.38,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know whose idea of a prank this is,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:52.31,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll make you sorry for all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:54.12,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate how vindictive I'll be,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.48,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,after the smile that charmed me that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.36,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to keep my promise to Emilia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.19,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get past that night!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:04.86,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Now, state your desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I have but one request.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hire me to work in this mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:11.95,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Hic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.78,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's how these looping plots work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:18.13,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Follow the same path, and you'll \Nend up in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.68,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,That's too large for you, Barusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:25.60,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,It appears nothing here will \Nfit except women's clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:28.46,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, alter that one for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:29.77,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:31.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Take my measurements, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:34.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A man can withstand all \Nkinds of awkwardness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:35.83,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,We'll measure you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:36.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:38.06,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me, Barusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to show me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:42.79,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,That can wait, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:45.39,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You'll help me with my work first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.07,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:52.28,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Retrace the same path I took yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:56.37,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I meant to do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:06:00.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is totally different from last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's like making a cheat sheet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:05.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but when you see the answers, \Nyou realize it's the wrong subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:07.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A total waste of effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:10.01,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, there! May I join—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.65,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, you may not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:13.26,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,This facility is part of my mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it is my property...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:17.43,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,I shall do with it as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:19.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why bother asking, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:22.67,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,My, how harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you seem not to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.99,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this bath is my property...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:30.78,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,But as part of my staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:35.15,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,are you not my property, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:36.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Chomp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:37.87,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,No hesitation at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:40.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is turning out different \Nfrom what I'd expected, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:44.67,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know what's bothering you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.59,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,but life is full of things \Nthat fail to go your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:49.10,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you think you'll be able to \Nget along with Ram and Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:54.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't spoken to Rem much yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:56.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but I get along fine with Ram.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:59.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I think she might be \Ngetting a little too friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she can work \Nas a maid that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:05.05,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Rem covers what Ram cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:07.12,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,As sisters, they must help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:10.86,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,In that sense, I think \Nthey get by quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ram is just the inferior \Nversion of her sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:16.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and all Rem does is cover for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:19.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And yet they insist Ram is superior \Nbecause she's older.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Their nerve is almost scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:27.33,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of nerve, yours appears \Nquite impressive, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:30.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I'm dizzy from that bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Roswaal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:36.27,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Cover up that sorry thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:37.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:41.85,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I was only waiting to help \NRoswaal-sama put on fresh clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:45.61,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to say that I've finished my bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I won't be changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't thinking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:52.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you spoil him too much! \NLet him dress himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:55.99,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I will not condone disrespect\N toward Roswaal-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.74,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I will use force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Any more, and I'll just \Nstir up a hornet's nest...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.33,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Barusu, \Ndo you have plans after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:05.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, just going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:08.80,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Then please wait in your room. \NI'll come by later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:10.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:12.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't mean anything... \NShe didn't mean anything by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Clear my mind, clear my mind! \NEmilia-tan is the only one for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:16.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:19.97,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,One Emilia-tan, two Emilia-tans, \Nthree Emilia-tans...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:21.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Am I in Heaven?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:23.39,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You're too noisy, Barusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:25.10,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,It's nighttime. Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Eep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.69,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Barusu, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:33.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, my heart's already set on \Nsomeone named "Emilia-tan"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:34.57,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:38.14,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to sit here, so I can \Nteach you to read and write.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's news to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But where's this coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:45.37,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell by watching you that \Nyou can't read or write.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:49.10,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't read or write, \NI can't send you shopping,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:51.24,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,and you can't write down orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:54.01,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start with this collection \Nof children's fairy tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:57.00,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tonight, I'll help \Nyou study every evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:59.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you being so nice to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:02.09,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Why else? It's so that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.54,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's so I can get off easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:06.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't correcting yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're never out of character, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:09.20,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Well, isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:11.23,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,The more you can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the less I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:16.89,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,And when I have less to do, so does Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:17.96,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,It's win-win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:20.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But that leaves me with piles of work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:23.50,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start with the basic i-glyphs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:26.70,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,After you master them, we'll move \Nto ro-glyphs and ha-glyphs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:28.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There are three different types?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hearing that is depressing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:32.84,SignA,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki Subaru \N\NOn the scene!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:32.84,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time to waste on doodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:36.21,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's an early start, so time's short.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleepy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:41.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say I dislike how you insert your \Nown feelings at the end, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:45.83,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I do believe honesty is my \Nmost charming feature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:47.14,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:53.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's so monotonous, I feel a Gestaltzerfall \Nphenomenon coming on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:59.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But still, even if it's to make your \Nlife easier, it makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:03.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I had the feeling \Nyou didn't like me much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:06.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll probably cause more problems \Nfor you down the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll try to become \Nuseful as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:20.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... I hate to admit it, but it's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:23.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Guess there's no need for my \Nsewing skills this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.79,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Sewing skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like sewing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:28.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:33.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, it looks like Ros-chi and \NEmilia-tan have lots of outfits,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't see any for you and Rem-rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:38.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to sew some for you? \NI'll take your measurements.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.74,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,That is unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These uniforms are all my sister and I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:46.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,How can you have nothing but those uniforms?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are all your clothes maid outfits?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:50.70,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,They cause no problems when we accompany \NRoswaal-sama on business,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:53.29,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,or when we work in the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:56.28,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,They also eliminate the need to explain \Nour place in the hierarchy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.71,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,which makes them very logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:00.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not about being logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to say cute girls
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have a duty to dress up, so they \Nplease the eyes of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.68,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,My sister is one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but no one would be happy to see me dress up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:13.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:16.37,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Would any good come of making you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:18.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I might take more pride in my work here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:20.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,which could boost my productivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:24.21,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what makes you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:27.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd also look forward to \Nseeing the differences
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:28.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,in your sartorial choices...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:30.47,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,That is none of your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:33.42,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Does my looking the same as my sister \Nsomehow inconvenience you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:37.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You love your sister way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:38.51,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:41.90,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know how to handle a knife, Barusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:46.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You hold the knife still and \Nturn the vegetable, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:52.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing when you \Nstare at me so intently...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.91,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Your unsightly appearance stands out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:12:00.56,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Especially your hair. It's very unrefined.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:04.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I did a pretty good job \Nof cutting it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:09.93,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, in this mansion, \NRem sees to everyone's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:14.23,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,She styles my hair and dresses me \Nevery morning, too. Isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Try to contribute a little, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:23.30,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:27.25,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,If you like, you can tidy up \NBarusu's hair a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:28.26,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having a girl mess with my hair \Nwill get me all worked up—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:35.76,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You keep looking at Barusu because \Nhis hair bothers you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:39.05,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:41.44,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I think combing it and evening out the ends
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would make him more presentable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:43.36,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.89,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You should take her up on her offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her hands will take you to paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:51.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound so dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:54.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to, \Nyou should just tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I don't want you to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:58.13,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,No, that isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.96,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is that it did \Nbother me a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,very much, a little... extremely, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:06.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, that proves the \Npoint that it bothers you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.90,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Betty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:09.75,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, Bubby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:12.35,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I have delicious \Nsweets today, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:14.12,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Eat them with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:15.85,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:21.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? Here to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:25.93,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is about what we \Ndiscussed at lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:29.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Lunchtime? Oh, about my hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You'll really style it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:34.36,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,No, I felt that I said some things \Nthat were uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:36.84,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I am very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:39.84,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,We may be colleagues, \Nbut as Emilia-sama's savior,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.48,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,your rank surpasses mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:44.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to put you through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:49.82,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should apologize for saying \Nsomething so pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:50.76,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Please forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:54.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's never that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:56.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes being human so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.65,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll give you a condition, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:04.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you agree to it, I'll forget \Neverything you just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:07.05,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,A condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:09.66,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, I shall hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:15.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you comb my hair a bit and even \Nout the ends, I'll let it slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:21.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,When you respond with silence, \Nit actually hurts even more...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.42,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It is just as Emilia-sama said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:29.18,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You have no ambition at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:31.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:34.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd think that'd make you fall for me \Nall over again, not disgust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:38.96,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,My sister said your eyes take on an obscene \Nlook when she's alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:43.21,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,So to be honest, I was prepared \Nto hear you suggest that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:44.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She's killing my reputation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.46,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I accept your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.74,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I shall do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:55.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after I keep my promise \Nto Emilia-tan would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.70,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:59.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I haven't made the promise yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:07.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Scoping out our date destination before I \Nmake the promise might be smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:10.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've researched places with the best views!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:11.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That just leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:13.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,...this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:13.08,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:14.34,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,He's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:15.68,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,And his face looks weird again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:19.07,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I need to make sure these guys don't find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:21.06,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by find you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.06,Default - upper,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Did you pee your pants?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.43,Default - upper,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,We're playing hide-and-seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:24.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Chill, brats! I played with you earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:25.72,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:26.83,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Play! Play!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:28.19,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Change your pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:29.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right, listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I come here, I'll be on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Try to take a hint, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:41.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll allow this little critter to play \Nwith Emilia-tan, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:47.34,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun, so this is where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.60,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:51.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:53.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All done shopping, Rem-rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.16,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it went quite smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.33,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, you're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:58.33,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:15:59.68,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,You have somewhere to go home to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.40,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You were quite popular with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:08.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, \Nkids have always liked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:12.54,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Like animals, children observe a hierarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:15.66,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,They can tell if it's all right \Nto belittle someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:18.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Those brats...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have no respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:25.00,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Did you show them anything \Nabout you worth respecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:27.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's a sound argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:31.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it doesn't seem right to \Nbelittle me from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:35.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ram seems like she'd handle \Nthat kind of thing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:36.67,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,My sister is wonderful, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:38.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'd think her personality
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:41.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,would cause conflict more often than not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:44.19,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's self-assured nature is \Nwhat makes her so charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:47.86,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot be that way at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:53.33,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how are your studies progressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:56.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just say I'm plugging along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ram is actually a pretty good teacher, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Though I wish she wouldn't sleep \Non my bed in mid-lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:04.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It kinda kills my motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:09.09,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,My sister only acts that way to \Nstimulate your motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:12.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have such absolute \Nfaith in your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:13.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally fanatical like a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.01,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Fanatical like a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:20.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's the demon version of divine possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds kinda cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:24.24,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:29.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, gods generally don't do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:32.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but demons will laugh along when \Nyou talk about future plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:34.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Especially for next year and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:36.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,They'll laugh their heads off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:48.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That smile is a million volts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.28,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell Emilia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:53.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying to hit on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.75,0:17:59.05,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Both Ram and Rem said they wouldn't \Nbe coming to see you tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:02.88,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,so I agreed to help with your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:05.31,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I can't do much, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:08.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm writing the basic i-glyphs \Nuntil I memorize them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:13.70,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You're studying a lot more \Nintensely than I imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:16.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,S-Since these fairy tales are aimed at kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:18.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,it's mostly i-glyphs, or so they said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:22.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So my goal for now is to \Nbe able... to read this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:26.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The moon sure is pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:31.26,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:35.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No! I mean, um, I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:39.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, I'll work \Nhard, and I'll study, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:42.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a date with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.72,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,What does a date entail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:49.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,When a guy and a girl go out alone \Ntogether, that's a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:53.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Only the goddess of love knows what \Nwill happen during that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:56.82,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means you went on a \Ndate with Rem today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:18:59.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! I didn't expect that response!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:01.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't count! Please don't count that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:05.95,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you want us to \Ngo out together, but where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:09.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's this really cute \Nlittle dog in the nearby village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:11.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's a flower field, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:14.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you in a field of flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:17.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and capture the image for \Neternity with my metia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:20.33,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um... The village, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:22.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The dog is super cute! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:28.48,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But it might cause trouble for \Nyou. And for the villagers—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:32.57,Default,SUbaru,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are so pure and innocent, \Nthey're like angels! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:36.23,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all right. You leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:37.51,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:40.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And the flower field is super colorful \Nand wonderfu— Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:46.14,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,If that will motivate you to work hard \Nfrom tomorrow on, then I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:49.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:53.12,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I bet the weather will be lovely tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:56.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... And it'll be a day I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.05,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again with...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:04.77,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You were just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:06.89,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:11.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it makes a guy really anxious \Nwhen you don't finish your sentences.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:14.05,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Subaru-kun the butler,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,remember to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:17.91,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Only those who work hard are rewarded,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so this will be a reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:02.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's settle this, fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:04.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't sleep tonight, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:07.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay awake to greet the \Nmorning of my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:14.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... What am I, a grade schooler who \Ncan't sleep before a class outing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:17.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Reminds me of when I overslept \Non the day of the class trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:23.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to retrace \Nthe same loop exactly,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:25.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but I got along well with Ram and Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:28.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I think I did better than last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:32.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything I feel I missed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.43,0:22:36.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,it's not saying goodnight to Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:39.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Each time I saw her, all we \Ndid was insult each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.53,0:22:45.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe I should have... \Nat least... thanked her...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.80,0:23:00.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:02.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:05.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No... Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.11,0:23:11.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.50,0:23:29.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.88,0:24:09.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What just...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.74,0:24:35.78,Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,The Morning of Our {\c&HFDD5AF&}Promise {\c&HFFFFFF&}Is Still Distant
